name: F16 Wings Sky War
description:
F16 Wings Sky War is one of the most exciting and thrilling action bushwhack adventure air fight war games, it involves the tactical fisticuffs dogfight between planes, fighter jets, skylanders and other war dragons. Train your commando jet fighter pilot hard and take full control of your air force fighter jet and fly high in the deep blue sky to eliminate all the assailant enemy threats.
Features
- Amazing Game Play Stunning Graphics
- Air Shooting Combat War Missions
- Different Aircraft to Choose From
- Wide Range of Missiles and Explosives
- Battle Ships and Enemy Bases
- Modern Aerial Combat
